Regulation (EEC) No 592/83 is hereby amended as follows:
1. in Article 1 (3), '1 November 1985' is replaced by '1 April 1986';
2. in Article 5 (2), '1 November 1983' is replaced by '1 March 1984';
3. in Article 5 (3), '1 January 1984' is replaced by '1 April 1984'.

Regulation (EEC) No 594/83 is hereby amended as follows:
1. in Article 1 (5), '1 November 1985' is replaced by '1 April 1986';
2. in Article 5 (2), '1 November 1983' is replaced by '1 March 1984';
3. in Article 5 (3), '1 January 1984' is replaced by '1 April 1984'.
